+# cloudflare_image_variant (Resource)
+
+
+
+## Example Usage
+
+```terraform
+resource "cloudflare_image_variant" "example_image_variant" {
+  account_id = "023e105f4ecef8ad9ca31a8372d0c353"
+  id = "hero"
+  options = {
+    fit = "scale-down"
+    height = 768
+    metadata = "none"
+    width = 1366
+  }
+  never_require_signed_urls = true
+}
+```
+
